10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T21:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打手係話電子付款唔一定係支那寶（唔好盲反）<br />\n但一定係話自己係支那用過支那寶同WeChat好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後話唔會介意用其他電子付款，只要「多個選擇」，到香港人話用多個選擇都唔用支那寶時，佢又loop返話香港落後過支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf184acb01575ce99c173c5942883abdf97807ef","tid":417520,"uid":79410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T21:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/mf/no.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; <br />\n打手係話電子付款唔一定係支那寶（唔好盲反）<br />\n但一定係話自己係支那用過支那寶同WeChat好用&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; <br />\n之後話唔會介意用其他電子付款，只要「多個選擇」，到香港人話用多個選擇都唔用支那寶時，佢又loop返話香港落後過支那&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/mf/z.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/mf/z.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/mf/z.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n同當年用母語教學＞取代英語教學。<br />\n然後再用普通話教學＞取代母語教學 <br />\n<br />\n同一道理，想用電子支付＞取代八達通/現金<br />\n然後再用支那寶＞取代電子支付<br />\n<br />\n用返同一招。"},{"pid":"07532ee400a4e077e463127ea32c3dcdee6cf952","tid":417520,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T21:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貼錢比我都唔用，一用拎撚曬你啲私人資料去賣</blockquote>支付寶/微信支付好似都可以用八達通方式匿名現金增值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261d422d01d3619311353b402577b06e2ed95000","tid":417520,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T21:30:09.000Z","msg":"其實成日咁驚人取代 自己做好d咪得囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4106c22d2d092569f636bb0c9427b9f61083ce44",