/>\n但廸士尼要植入RFID嚮手帶同四周裝感應器<br />\n相對地騰訊用微信平台已經省左一步</blockquote><br />\n睇到掃barcode就不了<br />\n80年代咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>掃bar code係付款<br />\n講緊係epayment唔值錢<br />\n而且咁多人搶同一舊屎 無肉分<br />\n<br />\n佢其他功能 例如泊左車比其他車擋住出唔到<br />\n依家只要影低對方個車牌<br />\n對方就會嚮電話即刻收到訊息叫佢移車<br />\n<br />\n呢d唔係科技創新 係點應用先令佢值錢<br />\n所以執著細既電子付款邊個先進根本無意義<br />\n佢地亦永遠無可能取代銀行系統或實物貨幣<br />\n<br />\n如果香港要追 係追後者<br />\n唔係既話遲早都係近水流台先得月<br />\n大部分香港人都係邊樣方便就用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/063734_b4b0c73ef9774449b7378be9fb691b9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F063734_b4b0c73ef9774449b7378be9fb691b9d.jpg&h=85e9bc65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好講其他野，答咗先</blockquote><br />\n中大一公佈左發現安全漏洞成班潛晒水<br />\n佢都未諗到點拆彈又點得閒答你問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfc0043fce54fb2a43f200a655a8a3bd2192e11","tid":417520,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0973584705a05ff5fb1bf981e0f531c6b238696","tid":417520,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩無用過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647c31c6b5e96b6b5a1bd2a1dcddcbb7ed0d66e8","tid":417520,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13e487ef82b537b2112d051f495ae50d4072fd5b","tid":417520,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:50:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93d32dcda995c0656ddc24cd769fa97c4225d699","tid":417520,"uid":38472,"lik